,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c97448d8970205a9fbd3b616510ca743c702bc7","tid":214064,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"咪生日快樂囉<br />\n係你鍾意佢咋，你諗咁多把鬼<br />\n人哋睇完諗都唔洗諗一句多謝就完咗個對話啦"},{"pid":"96d048fbeb91e31391e533944ea5a67cc8ab3dc0","tid":214064,"uid":97465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:19:14.000Z","msg":"曾經有一段真摯架感情係我前面，你會唔會有朝一日鍾意玩後面，生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3296345e5a119ebf9bd3a4e45d42f52ec5c5cd","tid":214064,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪生日快樂囉<br />\n係你鍾意佢咋，你諗咁多把鬼<br />\n人哋睇完諗都唔洗諗一句多謝就完咗個對話啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實上星期同佢講左幾句，我有提過佢就生日。<br />\n之後佢同我講下星期揾日食飯，但我唔想所以無應佢<br />\n我淨係希望佢同佢女朋友幸福，想講聲生日快樂。。"},{"pid":"374432b7637c0eced9fad9e77926a749dec5a3dd","tid":214064,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cbcf213d0dd4ebe54961c299b43e370c81120c","tid":214064,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HB</blockquote><br />\n鉛筆<br />\n<br />\n暗示佢幼過鉛筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8b1f74e1144ea671a711f5ca0effe813f7509b","tid":214064,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>HB</blockquote><br />\n鉛筆<br />\n<br />\n暗示佢幼過鉛筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n粗過司華力腸啊"},{"pid":"79f1c98e7ca3b7b28fa14345f6426ca4052759ca","tid":214064,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited